  "19-17": (
    caption: [Proton-motive force. The inner mitochondrial membrane separates two compartments of different \[H(cid:2)\], resulting in differences in chemical concentration (DpH) and charge distribution (Dc) across the membrane. The net effect is the proton-motive force (DG), which can be calculated as shown here. This is explained more fully in the text. c19OxidativePhosphorylationAndPhotophosphorylation.indd Page 745 27/09/12 1:34 PM user-F408 c19OxidativePhosphorylationAndPhotophosphorylation.indd Page 745 27/09/12 1:34 PM user-F408 /Users/user-F408/Desktop /Users/user-F408/Desktop],
